{"tid":965349,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"支持全球變暖，反對反全球暖化運動","createTime":"2019-01-02T03:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T03:47:16.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db8646b693eb03f217d0e747a40f645af5d6423f","tid":965349,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:25:34.000Z","msg":"香港天文台：1985至1995年，平均每日死亡人數<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/article/005wmonsoon.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Farticle%2F005wmonsoon.htm&d=MXhVha7Nm3DnEh1U5ZIZVtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=36433d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/article/005wmonsoon.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/article/005fig4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Farticle%2F005fig4a.jpg&h=97fb98ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n數據好明顯反映，冬天凍死人數，比夏天熱死人數多。<br />\n冬天死亡率明顯比夏天高。<br />\n而且香港還要是亞熱帶地區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.usatoday.com/amp/13323173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.usatoday.com%2Famp%2F13323173&d=MXhVha7Nm3DnEh1U5ZIZVtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=bec67ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://amp.usatoday.com/amp/13323173</a><br />\n<br />\n而在美國，與天氣相關的死亡事件中，<strong>63％係凍死</strong>，31％係熱死或中暑死，只有6％係因颱風暴雨而死。"},{"pid":"bad11b009b08b060333b29daad946cac3f73a4fa","tid":965349,"uid":51021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:27:22.000Z","msg":"租哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2019年又見<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0330c46ff6319a774183392e1b985d910f72e25","tid":965349,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:41:25.000Z","msg":"Time: Winter Kills Many More People Each Year Than Summer <br />\n<a href=\"http://time.com/3057652/season-deadly/\